00:30:07.250 --> 00:30:17.180 align:middle line:90%


00:30:17.180 --> 00:30:20.840 align:middle line:84%
And so one of the visions of
a planetary birth experience

00:30:20.840 --> 00:30:23.420 align:middle line:84%
would be enough
people in resonance,

00:30:23.420 --> 00:30:24.800 align:middle line:90%
in the feeling of love.

00:30:24.800 --> 00:30:29.290 align:middle line:90%


00:30:29.290 --> 00:30:32.770 align:middle line:84%
One greatest
influencers in my life,

00:30:32.770 --> 00:30:36.470 align:middle line:84%
