00:31:08.820 --> 00:31:12.967 align:middle line:84%
and I boldly said, would
you like some of this wine?

00:31:12.967 --> 00:31:16.630 align:middle line:90%


00:31:16.630 --> 00:31:20.490 align:middle line:84%
I had a question that
had really become

00:31:20.490 --> 00:31:23.330 align:middle line:90%
a driving force in my life.

00:31:23.330 --> 00:31:26.580 align:middle line:84%
And the question
