00:31:26.580 --> 00:31:31.620 align:middle line:84%
think is the meaning of all
this new power that's good?

00:31:31.620 --> 00:31:34.770 align:middle line:84%
And what is your
purpose in relationship

00:31:34.770 --> 00:31:37.410 align:middle line:90%
to this purpose of our power?

00:31:37.410 --> 00:31:41.070 align:middle line:84%
So I asked Earl
