00:31:46.710 --> 00:31:48.750 align:middle line:90%
I am an artist.

00:31:48.750 --> 00:31:53.460 align:middle line:84%
And I'm seeking a new image of
man commensurate with our power

00:31:53.460 --> 00:31:55.890 align:middle line:90%
to shape the future.

00:31:55.890 --> 00:31:57.390 align:middle line:90%
And it flashed in my mind--

00:31:57.390 --> 00:31:59.274 align:middle line:90%
I'm going to marry you.

00:31:59.274 --> 00:32:00.690 align:middle line:90%
