a head-on crash.

00:32:18.300 --> 00:32:21.240 align:middle line:84%
But that was the
expectation of the day.

00:32:21.240 --> 00:32:23.770 align:middle line:90%


00:32:23.770 --> 00:32:26.590 align:middle line:10%
We lived in Lime
Rock, Connecticut.

00:32:26.590 --> 00:32:30.250 align:middle line:10%
Earl worked on his art
