00:32:30.250 --> 00:32:32.800 align:middle line:90%


00:32:32.800 --> 00:32:36.870 align:middle line:84%
Suddenly, I found myself
in Lime Rock, Connecticut,

00:32:36.870 --> 00:32:44.440 align:middle line:84%
pregnant in a little one-room
house with an artist husband.

00:32:44.440 --> 00:32:47.460 align:middle line:84%
And I remember waking
up saying, well,

00:32:47.460 --> 00:32:50.020 align:middle line:90%
where did Barbara Marx go?

00:32:50.020 --> 00:32:54.060 align:middle line:90%


00:32:54.060 --> 00:32:57.260 align:middle line:84%
When you think of a woman like
me having five children that I

00:32:57.260 --> 00:33:00.650 align:middle line:84%
