00:33:00.650 --> 00:33:02.540 align:middle line:84%
the children every
day to school,

00:33:02.540 --> 00:33:05.240 align:middle line:84%
every day to the frog pond,
every day to this, read

00:33:05.240 --> 00:33:07.790 align:middle line:84%
to them, loved them, they
were the joy of my life,

00:33:07.790 --> 00:33:12.320 align:middle line:84%
but it didn't even touch the
part of me that has vocation.

00:33:12.320 --> 00:33:15.240 align:middle line:10%
>> And she said, I
can't do this anymore.

00:33:15.240 --> 00:33:20.560 align:middle line:10%
I can't give my life
over to simply the PTA.

00:33:20.560 --> 00:33:23.890 align:middle line:10%
>> And that's about what she
