00:33:26.260 --> 00:33:29.050 align:middle line:84%
And I think Salk particularly,
and to a certain extent,

00:33:29.050 --> 00:33:31.325 align:middle line:84%
Maslow, both
acknowledged that there

00:33:31.325 --> 00:33:33.700 align:middle line:84%
was something going on in her
head that was really vital.

00:33:33.700 --> 00:33:44.760 align:middle line:90%


00:33:44.760 --> 00:33:49.410 align:middle line:84%
>> Jonas Salk was the famous
inventor of the polio vaccine.

00:33:49.410 --> 00:33:51.930 align:middle line:84%
He was starting
the Salk Institute,

00:33:51.930 --> 00:33:57.000 align:middle line:84%
which would study how science
could help transform humanity.

00:33:57.000 --> 00:34:00.030 align:middle line:84%
I was immediately
drawn in by a project

00:34:00.030 --> 00:34:03.240 align:middle line:90%
