00:34:03.240 --> 00:34:07.070 align:middle line:84%
I began to write the letter
as to what that should be.

00:34:07.070 --> 00:34:09.600 align:middle line:84%
It should be a place
we can celebrate

00:34:09.600 --> 00:34:12.810 align:middle line:84%
the emergence of the next
stage of human evolution.

00:34:12.810 --> 00:34:15.520 align:middle line:84%
And about two weeks
later, a phone rang.

00:34:15.520 --> 00:34:16.320 align:middle line:90%
Mrs. Hubbard?

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:17.290 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:34:17.290 --> 00:34:20.820 align:middle line:90%
He said, this is Dr. Salk.

00:34:20.820 --> 00:34:25.020 align:middle line:84%
I read your description
of The Theater of Man.

00:34:25.020 --> 00:34:28.839 align:middle line:84%
You have stated my vision
better than I could.

00:34:28.839 --> 00:34:30.570 align:middle line:90%
Could I take you to lunch?

00:34:30.570 --> 00:34:33.190 align:middle line:90%


00:34:33.190 --> 00:34:35.360 align:middle line:84%
