00:35:43.250 --> 00:35:48.980 align:middle line:10%
One day I was taking a walk
in the hills above my home.

00:35:48.980 --> 00:35:52.100 align:middle line:10%
I'd been doing a lot of
reading about the great mystics

00:35:52.100 --> 00:35:55.820 align:middle line:10%
and spiritual teachers of
the past in relationship

00:35:55.820 --> 00:35:58.860 align:middle line:10%
to a positive
future for humanity.

00:35:58.860 --> 00:36:01.760 align:middle line:84%
