all of my thoughts together.

00:36:01.760 --> 00:36:04.400 align:middle line:90%


00:36:04.400 --> 00:36:10.010 align:middle line:84%
Frustrated, I suddenly
stopped and posed a question

00:36:10.010 --> 00:36:12.690 align:middle line:90%
to the universe--

00:36:12.690 --> 00:36:15.950 align:middle line:90%
what is humanity's new story?

00:36:15.950 --> 00:36:20.000 align:middle line:84%
In a flash, I was
catapulted into the future

00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:25.970 align:middle line:84%
and I could see a few frames
ahead in the movie of creation.

00:36:25.970 --> 00:36:28.700 align:middle line:84%
I was looking at
Earth from space

00:36:28.700 --> 00:36:31.610 align:middle line:84%
and I was a member of
Earth simultaneously.

00:36:31.610 --> 00:36:33.530 align:middle line:84%
And Earth was,
[GASPS] struggling

00:36:33.530 --> 00:36:35.390 align:middle line:84%
