out of energy.

00:36:35.390 --> 00:36:36.950 align:middle line:90%
I could feel the pain.

00:36:36.950 --> 00:36:40.280 align:middle line:10%
At one point, there was
a moment of shared pain

00:36:40.280 --> 00:36:43.800 align:middle line:10%
so great that we stopped.

00:36:43.800 --> 00:36:48.260 align:middle line:84%
And in that moment of stopping,
through pain came empathy,

00:36:48.260 --> 00:36:50.920 align:middle line:84%
came love, very
much like we've had

00:36:50.920 --> 00:36:56.270 align:middle line:84%
