tsunamis or hurricanes.

00:36:56.270 --> 00:36:59.480 align:middle line:90%
But usually, that empathy stops.

00:36:59.480 --> 00:37:01.580 align:middle line:90%
This time, it didn't stop.

00:37:01.580 --> 00:37:05.810 align:middle line:84%
>> And so she had a
mystical experience,

00:37:05.810 --> 00:37:07.730 align:middle line:90%
which was not unusual.

00:37:07.730 --> 00:37:10.310 align:middle line:84%
She's had many, but
this was potent.

00:37:10.310 --> 00:37:16.580 align:middle line:10%
>> I felt every basic social
system shift simultaneously

00:37:16.580 --> 00:37:20.090 align:middle line:10%
as innovations and
breakthroughs connected.

00:37:20.090 --> 00:37:24.710 align:middle line:84%
Systems of health and education,
economics and environment

00:37:24.710 --> 00:37:27.140 align:middle line:90%
began to coalesce seamlessly.

00:37:27.140 --> 00:37:32.660 align:middle line:84%
>> It was a vision like a film,
where we began to coordinate

00:37:32.660 --> 00:37:35.975 align:middle line:84%
and help each other
and live with empathy.

00:37:35.975 --> 00:37:40.720 align:middle line:84%
>> I think I had a quick
glimpse of what's actually true.

00:37:40.720 --> 00:37:43.040 align:middle line:84%
It's we are a
living system and we

00:37:43.040 --> 00:37:46.220 align:middle line:84%
