00:38:00.690 --> 00:38:06.240 align:middle line:10%
we had power with our dad, who
was loving but also had rage,

00:38:06.240 --> 00:38:07.740 align:middle line:10%
like Jehovah.

00:38:07.740 --> 00:38:14.760 align:middle line:84%
And our mother, who was
very loving, but not potent.

00:38:14.760 --> 00:38:17.760 align:middle line:84%
And Barbara, in this
vision, saw humanity

00:38:17.760 --> 00:38:24.980 align:middle line:84%
combining our powers with
love, empathy, and creativity.

00:38:24.980 --> 00:38:28.710 align:middle line:84%
>> And in that moment,
I heard the words,

00:38:28.710 --> 00:38:32.235 align:middle line:90%
