00:38:41.860 --> 00:38:44.690 align:middle line:90%
Go tell this story, Barbara.

00:38:44.690 --> 00:38:58.300 align:middle line:90%


00:38:58.300 --> 00:39:00.250 align:middle line:90%
>> She got her marching orders.

00:39:00.250 --> 00:39:06.790 align:middle line:10%
She was determined to go forth
in this bold, courageous way

00:39:06.790 --> 00:39:11.110 align:middle line:10%
to do whatever she needed to
do, to talk to who ever she

00:39:11.110 --> 00:39:15.910 align:middle line:10%
needed to talk to, to tell
people, to be that messenger.

00:39:15.910 --> 00:39:20.560 align:middle line:84%
>> The new story of the
evolution of our species with

00:39:20.560 --> 00:39:24.670 align:middle line:84%
us becoming conscious
