00:39:24.670 --> 00:39:26.410 align:middle line:90%
I'd been looking for.

00:39:26.410 --> 00:39:29.770 align:middle line:10%
And I then decided to
write a book called

00:39:29.770 --> 00:39:33.760 align:middle line:10%
"Conscious Evolution: Awakening
the Power of Our Social

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:34.630 align:middle line:10%
Potential."

