social potential movement,

00:39:41.110 --> 00:39:43.130 align:middle line:90%
or the self-actualizing society.

00:39:43.130 --> 00:39:54.360 align:middle line:90%


00:39:54.360 --> 00:39:56.310 align:middle line:90%
>> No, I'm really excited.

00:39:56.310 --> 00:39:58.920 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, a production meeting
is a place where you destroy

00:39:58.920 --> 00:40:01.132 align:middle line:10%
everything you've made before.

