happens to coincide

01:09:04.260 --> 01:09:08.536 align:middle line:84%
with her personal birthday,
so 83 years old and rocking it

01:09:08.536 --> 01:09:11.242 align:middle line:90%
out, Barbara Marx Hubbard.

