[APPLAUSE]

01:09:48.735 --> 01:09:58.840 align:middle line:90%


01:09:58.840 --> 01:10:01.880 align:middle line:10%
>> December 22nd, 2012--

01:10:01.880 --> 01:10:04.880 align:middle line:10%
if you're watching this
video, it means one thing--

01:10:04.880 --> 01:10:07.680 align:middle line:10%
the world didn't end yesterday.

01:10:07.680 --> 01:10:10.576 align:middle line:10%
According to media reports of
an ancient Mayan prophecy--

01:10:10.576 --> 01:10:13.700 align:middle line:10%


01:10:13.700 --> 01:10:16.470 align:middle line:10%
>> She would like to have seen
something in the news about

01:10:16.470 --> 01:10:19.860 align:middle line:10%
people recognizing
that it's a new time.

01:10:19.860 --> 01:10:25.880 align:middle line:10%
But once the day passed,
it was like, silent.

01:10:25.880 --> 01:10:29.180 align:middle line:84%
And there was no
public expression

01:10:29.180 --> 01:10:33.020 align:middle line:84%
of a birth that had happened
and that something had shifted,

01:10:33.020 --> 01:10:37.130 align:middle line:84%
and that this was a new time,
we are moving into another epic.

01:10:37.130 --> 01:10:41.880 align:middle line:84%
And I think she looked for
that to be the new news.

01:10:41.880 --> 01:10:44.510 align:middle line:90%
And it just wasn't there.

01:10:44.510 --> 01:10:47.240 align:middle line:84%
>> I think by 2012, the
mainstream news media was

01:10:47.240 --> 01:10:49.430 align:middle line:84%
so sick of all these New
Age prophecies that they

01:10:49.430 --> 01:10:51.055 align:middle line:84%
didn't really pay
much attention to it.

01:10:51.055 --> 01:10:55.670 align:middle line:10%
>> She felt that this was a
fulfillment of her mission.

01:10:55.670 --> 01:10:59.180 align:middle line:84%
She was telling the
story of our birth,

01:10:59.180 --> 01:11:03.560 align:middle line:84%
and then not much
happened afterwards.

01:11:03.560 --> 01:11:07.020 align:middle line:84%
And she was exhausted,
also, physically.

01:11:07.020 --> 01:11:09.710 align:middle line:84%
And I think that the
fact that there wasn't

01:11:09.710 --> 01:11:13.400 align:middle line:84%
this magical transformation
that she believed

01:11:13.400 --> 01:11:17.000 align:middle line:84%
would happen, really happen,
that something big would

01:11:17.000 --> 01:11:21.200 align:middle line:84%
happen, momentous would
happen, it was very depressing

01:11:21.200 --> 01:11:23.690 align:middle line:84%
and she didn't know
what next to do.

01:11:23.690 --> 01:11:25.640 align:middle line:84%
And when Barbara
doesn't know what

01:11:25.640 --> 01:11:27.890 align:middle line:84%
next to do for her
mission, there's

01:11:27.890 --> 01:11:33.090 align:middle line:84%
a tremendous pain way beyond
what I think most of us feel.

01:11:33.090 --> 01:11:43.380 align:middle line:90%


01:11:43.380 --> 01:11:46.680 align:middle line:90%
>> I am depressed.

01:11:46.680 --> 01:11:55.690 align:middle line:84%
I have doubt as to whether it
is possible for people's effort,

01:11:55.690 --> 01:11:59.840 align:middle line:84%
including my own, to
make a difference.

01:11:59.840 --> 01:12:03.644 align:middle line:84%
I have lost my
arrow of evolution.

