We experienced the
birth and we have

01:12:29.950 --> 01:12:32.270 align:middle line:90%
a global moment of oneness.

01:12:32.270 --> 01:12:35.660 align:middle line:90%
It was experienced by all of us.

01:12:35.660 --> 01:12:37.730 align:middle line:84%
And then we were like,
where's the baby?

01:12:37.730 --> 01:12:38.935 align:middle line:90%
Where's the baby?

01:12:38.935 --> 01:12:41.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Many of the students were
right there with Barbara.

01:12:41.420 --> 01:12:43.940 align:middle line:10%
They were in a
state of confusion.

