How do you fund them?

01:13:17.270 --> 01:13:18.680 align:middle line:84%
How do you get
them into society?

01:13:18.680 --> 01:13:20.810 align:middle line:90%
How do you communicate them?

01:13:20.810 --> 01:13:25.970 align:middle line:84%
That, to me, is the difference
between activism and sort

01:13:25.970 --> 01:13:29.630 align:middle line:84%
of self-congratulatory
magical thinking.

01:13:29.630 --> 01:13:49.010 align:middle line:90%


