01:14:37.430 --> 01:14:40.130 align:middle line:84%
>> Our father's pronouncement
that he kept saying--

01:14:40.130 --> 01:14:42.020 align:middle line:90%
do your best.

01:14:42.020 --> 01:14:45.830 align:middle line:84%
That has been a real motivating
force to do her best.

01:14:45.830 --> 01:14:50.330 align:middle line:10%
>> I don't think, in any way,
